OL,3,CDrug smuggler claims he was carrying
OL,4,Csombreros in suitcase from Mexico
OL,6,FA man who attempted to smuggle almost
OL,7,F#6 million worth of cocaine into the
OL,8,FUK said he had only brought sombreros
OL,9,Fback from his trip.
OL,11,F35-year-old Kristopher Purvis, from
OL,12,FDurham, was arrested after he landed
OL,13,Fat Edinburgh airport on a flight from
OL,14,FMexico City via Paris.
