OL,3,CDrug smuggler claims he was carrying
OL,4,Csombreros in suitcase from Mexico
OL,6,FPurvis, who was carrying a black
OL,7,Fsuitcase and a bag of Mexican sombrero
OL,8,Fsouvenir hats, was stopped by Border
OL,9,FForce officers in the airport. He told
OL,10,Fofficers he had returned to the UK
OL,11,Fwith only the souvenir hats, but when
OL,12,Fhis luggage was searched, a total of
OL,13,F48 kilos of cocaine was found.
OL,15,FInvestigators from the Organised Crime
OL,16,FPartnership, made up of National Crime
OL,17,FAgency and Police Scotland officers,
OL,18,Fsaid the drugs would have been worth
OL,19,Fup to #5.64 million at street value.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
