OL,4,Csombreros in suitcase from Mexico
OL,6,FPurvis pleaded guilty to the
OL,7,Fimportation and being concerned in the
OL,8,Fsupply of Class A drugs. He was
OL,9,Fsentenced at Edinburgh High Court on 4
OL,10,FMarch and jailed for 10 years.
OL,12,FA second male was also arrested at the
OL,13,Ftime who pleaded not guilty to the
OL,14,Fsame charges. A trial date has been
OL,15,Fset for 10 November in relation to his
OL,16,Falleged involvement.
