OL,6,FDonnie Lawrie, from the NCA, said:
OL,7,F"Kristopher Purvis attempted to appear
OL,8,Flike an innocuous tourist and claimed
OL,9,Fto only be carrying sombrero
OL,10,Fsouvenirs. The truth was, the luggage
OL,11,Fhe was carrying contained millions of
OL,12,Fpounds worth of drugs."
