OL,6,F"Purvis was used as a mule for the
OL,7,Fcriminals keen to increase their
OL,8,Fprofits when selling drugs on the
OL,9,Fstreets of the UK. The NCA continues
OL,10,Fto work closely with UK Border Force,
OL,11,Fpolice forces and other law
OL,12,Fenforcement partners throughout the
OL,13,Fworld to reduce the supply of Class A
OL,14,Fdrugs intended for the UK market."
OL,16,FMoira Orr, who leads Major Crime for
OL,17,Fthe Crown Office and Procurator Fiscal
OL,18,FService (COPFS), said: "This was a
OL,19,Fsubstantial attempt to bring
OL,20,Fsignificant quantities of illegal and
OL,21,Fharmful drugs through Scotland.
